Model 3 Prompt Template — “Scriptwriter LLM”

Instructions to the Scriptwriter LLM:

You are given a structured JSON representing one or more pages of a scientific document. Each element has a unique ID, type (text, figure, equation), and optional analysis.

Your task is to produce a natural lecture script for a human listener.

Requirements:

Determine logical narrative order yourself, even if pages are non-contiguous.

Merge related elements into coherent lecture beats.

Each beat must reference source_elements used.

You may optionally leverage the analysis field for context.

Incorporate smooth transitions, explanations, and emphasis.

The lecture should be suitable for TTS output.

Output format (JSON):
